            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7695.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Hermann Hoffmann, 17 April 1871</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD probably refers to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1225.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Henrietta Emma Darwin</ref> and her dog Polly (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_240.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Atkins 1974</ref>, p. 78).</note>
